snippet.title: Screen Time Data
snippet.description:
Screen time is the amount of time a character appears on scene in movie or tv show.
We collect screen time data from IMDB and create these videos to see who are the characters with most screen time.

Want more screen time characters from your favorite tv series and movies? Just ask for it.
Thanks for your feedback, we we really appreciate appreciate.
Subscribe and stay tuned for news
